highlights.text: “LA CANCIÓN” by J Balvin and Bad Bunny has been on Top Songs Mexico the longest, at 327 weeks straight.
“CRIPTONITA” by Tito Double P is the highest new entry on Top Songs Mexico at #35.
Fuerza Regida has the most spots on Top Songs Mexico. “Marlboro Rojo” is the highest at #2.
“Azul” by Zoé is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Mexico, up 48 spots at #133.
